OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMental health: Lowri       
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FMiller's mother says       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fhospital failed her        
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A bereaved mother said her daughter was
OL,6, "failed miserably" by a mental health  
OL,7, service now under review by inspectors.
OL,9,FSue Miller feels Lowri, 32, should not 
OL,10,Fhave been discharged from the Royal    
OL,11,FGlamorgan Hospital in Rhondda Cynon    
OL,12,FTaf. She died the next day.            
OL,14,FHealthcare Inspectorate Wales (HIW) is 
OL,15,Freviewing the mental health service in 
OL,16,FCwm Taf Morgannwg Health Board over    
OL,17,Fconcerns about discharges.             
OL,19,FThe health board said it would "take on
OL,20,Fboard" any HIW recommendations.        
